{
 "name": "RPlog_Some_New_Help",
 "title": "Some New Help",
 "summary": "Aboard the NRCV Audacity over plague-stricken Dac, the exhausted Senator Lemos receives a neutral Caspian relief mission led by Lt Commander Lynae Cassius, a doctor and biological-warfare expert, accompanied by her second Lieutenant Sadim Gnik, the Twi'lek engineer Sub Lieutenant Ven Secura, and the droid HM-743. Cassius, who openly acknowledges her past role in the Cochran bombing, offers the Caspian Democratic Union's expertise and quarantine facilities to help find a cure for the contagion ravaging the planet. Lemos gratefully accepts, prioritizing his people's survival over politics, and the two coordinate plans to set the medical ship Reannon Calder down planetside, gather infection samples, and slot into the existing relief efforts as an independent body. After discussing the ad-hoc relief network and Lemos's caution about the jumpy local military, the Caspians take their leave to begin work.",
